    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unfoldink</strong> 是一款 <strong>2D 逻辑解谜冒险</strong> 游戏，你可以 <strong>创造独特的卡牌组合</strong>，制作 <strong>动画故事</strong>，解释部落的离去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252250/extras/8d12def6b832ce4481ea48bd63105152.poster.avif?t=1756738786\" width=800 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252250/extras/8d12def6b832ce4481ea48bd63105152.webm?t=1756738786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252250/extras/8d12def6b832ce4481ea48bd63105152.mp4?t=1756738786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>UNFOLDINK 提供</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-&gt; <strong>独特</strong>的烧脑谜题</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-&gt; 总共有 <strong>11 种不同的卡牌</strong> 和……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252250/extras/dda3c1385d468089d91f9a59e2540ce1.avif?t=1756738786\" width=874 height=492 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >……超过 <strong>160 种动画组合</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-&gt; 有趣的角色 <strong>互动</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252250/extras/16c4319d8dad0c1184ca91de68c7742f.poster.avif?t=1756738786\" width=784 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252250/extras/16c4319d8dad0c1184ca91de68c7742f.webm?t=1756738786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252250/extras/16c4319d8dad0c1184ca91de68c7742f.mp4?t=1756738786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-&gt; 控制动物、猎人和地点</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-&gt; <strong>易于理解的玩法</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-&gt; <strong>45 到 60 分钟</strong> 的游戏时长</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252250/extras/978927a281683fe8343991b72cb9d007.poster.avif?t=1756738786\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252250/extras/978927a281683fe8343991b72cb9d007.webm?t=1756738786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252250/extras/978927a281683fe8343991b72cb9d007.mp4?t=1756738786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>原创故事</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>亚马逊雨林中的一个古老部落留下了他们为什么离开营地的线索。他们是被迫离开，还是主动想离开？使用他们留下的卡牌，通过 <strong>各种</strong> <strong>组合</strong>，拼凑出 <strong>究竟发生了什么</strong> 的故事。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252250/extras/a9bd6334a8794dc5e4fda7b721b1c86e.poster.avif?t=1756738786\" width=800 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252250/extras/a9bd6334a8794dc5e4fda7b721b1c86e.webm?t=1756738786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252250/extras/a9bd6334a8794dc5e4fda7b721b1c86e.mp4?t=1756738786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252250/extras/4bd345351c182eed7f2224af45b49c4d.poster.avif?t=1756738786\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252250/extras/4bd345351c182eed7f2224af45b49c4d.webm?t=1756738786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252250/extras/4bd345351c182eed7f2224af45b49c4d.mp4?t=1756738786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开笔墨下的真相，是时候了。 <strong>许多人</strong> 曾经尝试过，但 <strong>你是唯一一个</strong> 能破解这个 <strong>谜团</strong> 的人。</p>",
